Описание занятия: 1. Read this article on answering tricky interview questions: 
https://www.thebalancemoney.com/worst-interview-answers-2061232
Be prepared to discuss it in the next class


Look at the questions again:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/18LWCsH-LkMREJEIyeLcRXSzNs-Z80qBI/view
Prepare good answers to the questions. You can write the answers down or just think of what you can say.
You will use your answers on our next lesson.


1) Why should we hire you?
2) What are your strengths?
3) Can you share a weakness?
4) Tell me about your last job
5) Why have you decided to apply for this position?

